        <section id="opportunity" class="py-20 md:py-24 text-center bg-slate-100">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
                <h2 class="section-title">What is the AI Chasm?</h2>
                <div class="section-subtitle">
                    <p>The generative AI landscape presents a fundamental paradox:</p>
                    <p class="font-semibold text-slate-800 my-2">immense power coupled with inherent unreliability.</p>
                    <p>This lack of verifiable authenticity creates a critical trust deficit, preventing the technology's use in high-stakes professional environments. The result is a clear and urgent market opportunity for specialized, accountable AI agents capable of delivering vetted, expert-driven insights.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="mt-16 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-left">
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-2 border-red-200">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-red-600">AI Limitations</h3>
                        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-slate-600">
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 text-red-500">❌</span>Remains Gullible.</li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 text-red-500">❌</span>Lacks Verifiable Authenticity.</li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 text-red-500">❌</span>Disclaims All Accountability.</li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 text-red-500">❌</span>Spreads Misinformation.</li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 text-red-500">❌</span>Delivers Unattributed Content.</li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 text-red-500">❌</span>Degrades Trust in High-Stakes Decisions.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-2 border-sky-500">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-sky-700">Our Sustainable Advantage</h3>
                         <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-slate-600">
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 text-green-500">✅</span>Leverages Licensed Expert Content.</li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 text-green-500">✅</span>Guarantees Verifiable Source Lineage.</li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 text-green-500">✅</span>Operates with Full Accountability.</li>
                            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 text-green-500">✅</span>Delivers Authentic, Data-Driven Advice.</li>
