        <section id="technology" class="py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-center">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
                <h2 class="section-title">Architecture Wins Technology Wars</h2>
                <div class="section-subtitle">
                    <p>Our platform is built on open source and well-understood protocols. We begin by ingesting licensed content from verifiable experts, which is then structured in a Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) system. This curated knowledge base powers our specialized AI agents.</p>
                    <p class="mt-4">Internally, our agents collaborate through an **Agent-to-Agent (A2A)** protocol to combine their expertise. Externally, our **Multi-platform Communication Protocol (MCP)** acts as a universal translator, allowing major platforms to query our agents for trusted answers, creating a powerful revenue-sharing model.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="mt-16 p-8 bg-slate-100 rounded-2xl">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">From Verifiable Content to Global Distribution</h3>
